# ThinkTank Demo - Environment Configuration

# =============================================================================
# REQUIRED: Claude API Configuration
# =============================================================================

# Your Claude API key from https://console.anthropic.com/
CLAUDE_API_KEY=your-claude-api-key-here

# =============================================================================
# OPTIONAL: Model Configuration
# =============================================================================

# Claude model version (default: claude-sonnet-4-20250514)
# Uncomment to use a different version:
# CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929  # For Sonnet 4.5
# CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-opus-4-20250514      # For Opus 4 (when available)

# =============================================================================
# Instructions
# =============================================================================

# 1. Copy this file to .env:
#    cp .env.example .env
#
# 2. Edit .env and add your actual Claude API key
#
# 3. Never commit .env to version control (it's in .gitignore)
#
# 4. To use environment variables, either:
#    a) Use python-dotenv (pip install python-dotenv)
#    b) Export manually: export CLAUDE_API_KEY="your-key"
#
# 5. Alternatively, set directly in terminal:
#    export CLAUDE_API_KEY="your-api-key-here"
#    python demo.py
